# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:101
msgid "Aspect Ratio"
msgstr "Hlutfall"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:101
msgid ""
"The aspect ratio of the final exported video. 1920×1080 reduces to 16:9. "
"This also takes into account the pixel ratio, for example 2:1 rectangular "
"pixels will affect the aspect ratio."
msgstr ""
"Hlutfall lokaútfluttra vídeóa. 1920×1080 jafngildir 16:9. Þetta tekur einnig "
"tillit til pixlahlutfalls, til dæmis hafa 2:1 rétthyrnd pixlar áhrif á "
"hlutfallið."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:102
msgid "Pixel Ratio"
msgstr "Pixlahlutfall"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:102
msgid ""
"The ratio representing pixel shape. Most video profiles use a 1:1 square "
"pixel shape, but others will use rectangular pixels."
msgstr ""
"Hlutfall sem táknar lögun pixla. Flest vídeóprófílar nota 1:1 ferkantaða "
"pixla, en aðrir nota rétthyrnda pixla."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:103
msgid "Frame Rate"
msgstr "Rammatíðni"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:103
msgid "The frequency that the frames will be displayed at."
msgstr "Tíðni sem rammar eru sýndir á."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:104
msgid "Interlaced"
msgstr "Skiptir rammar"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:104
msgid ""
"Is this format used on alternating scan lines (i.e. broadcast and analog "
"formats)"
msgstr ""
"Er þetta snið notað á skiptum skönnunar línum (t.d. útsendingar- og analóg "
"snið)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:105
msgid "Spherical"
msgstr "Kúlulaga"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:105
msgid ""
"When enabled, injects spherical 360° metadata (SV3D atom) into the exported "
"file so compatible players immediately recognize it as a 360° video."
msgstr ""
"Þegar virkjað, bætir við kúlulaga 360° metadata (SV3D atom) í útflutta skrá "
"svo samhæfð spilunarforrit þekki hana strax sem 360° myndband."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
